{"tid":2358334,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Michael Burry：Tesla是泡沫，排放積分不代表盈利能力","createTime":"2021-01-08T05:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T12:09:53.000Z","uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"720e25aaf47a286464cf61732650263af062123c","tid":2358334,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2761370/TSLA_ModelS_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2761370%2FTSLA_ModelS_600.jpg&h=8ce738a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特斯拉（Tesla，美：TSLA）「電池日」發布會未能令市場滿意，Tesla周三股價大跌一成。美國對沖基金經理、《沽注一擲（The Big Short）》原型Michael Burry 本周連發帖文質疑Tesla，Burry 指，Telsa 以外的全球汽車行業市銷率（Price-to-Sales）僅0.35倍，而Tesla 為18倍，標籤Tesla為泡沫。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Burry指，Tesla以外的全球汽車年銷售額2.3萬億美元，EBIT（息稅前利潤）1000億美元，總市值8070億美元。與此相比，Tesla銷售額為250億美元，沒有EBIT，市值4380億美元，形容Tesla在排放監管積分收入（regulatory credit）是「正在融化的冰塊」。<br />\n<br />\n他在另一帖文指，Tesla 出售「排放監管積分」賺取收入，不一定集團具盈利能力，指Tesla 收入、交付數目在今年內無增長，若撇除排放積分收入，首兩季更錄經營虧損，再次形容Tesla為泡沫。<br />\n<br />\nMichael Burry被視為2007、08年首批發現美國次貸危機即將爆發的投資者之一，並在從看淡房貸債務擔保證券獲厚利。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2761370/【Tesla股價】《沽注一擲》原型Michael%20Burry：Tesla是泡沫%E3%80%80排放積分不代表盈利能力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2761370%2F%E3%80%90Tesla%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E6%B2%BD%E6%B3%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%93%B2%E3%80%8B%E5%8E%9F%E5%9E%8BMichael%2520Burry%EF%BC%9ATesla%E6%98%AF%E6%B3%A1%E6%B2%AB%25E3%2580%2580%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%8D%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTITMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=6d7ce844\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2761370/【Tesla股價】《沽注一擲》原型Michael%20Burry：Tesla是泡沫%E3%80%80排放積分不代表盈利能力</a></span>"},{"pid":"121aaca0dffbef875269737